snippet.textDisplay: What are they trying to say ? If you spend $100k in modifying your defender , upgraded suspension , stiffened chassis ,  roll cages , bracing everywhere you too can batter the hell out of your £80,000 car so it’s barely fit for a skip . Note the roll over at the end , smashed the front right wishbone , scrub back and forth and you see the movie cuts and then restarts with car in different position , front right wheel went banana shaped on impact . LR trying so hard to try convince this is a replacement for the old defender and just as tough , nope , take that thing serious off roading and you’ll be collecting all the plastic bits and sparkly things in a plastic bag afterwards and a horrendous repair bill , should have called it a discovery evolution or something cus it ain’t no defender .
